{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 391.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At this point, Lithuania is under Russian control, and therefore is not-- doesn't pose the same immediate danger that being under the Germans does.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you have any idea how they had done their money?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What they did-- how they had traveling--?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My impression is that what happened was they took some jewelry with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably as much money as they could get their hands on quickly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think a lot of stuff had been frozen by the Polish government once the war began, so you couldn't take stuff out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't think it's like they've been able to take vast amounts, but I think enough, you know, for the bribes or to get-- buy-- that ride on the hay truck.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean the wagon that will get you out of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to get to Lithuania-- to make the journey-- I do remember, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tremendous amount of traveling at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sleds.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is with Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which month-- what month were we at now?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well by this time, we must be obviously in winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] You know, the war has started when?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the summer of that year, or late summer, or August--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--or something?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This must be the winter of that year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember it being so cold at night that my parents make my sister and me stand on the runners of the sled from time to time-- on the back-- because there's the fear that if we fall asleep, we may not wake up.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
